synopsis.native: Sabina vive con y de sus padres en sus treinta años. Otra "artista" que se arrastra por un Madrid en crisis, rodeada de gente aún más triste y peor que ella.
synopsis.english: Sabina lives with and from her parents in her thirties. Another "artist" who drags herself through a Madrid in crisis, surrounded by people even sadder and worst than herself. Chance gives him the opportunity to "kill it" - and why not?
